  Locus:
    Page: 204
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Grace
---
Grace is always sufficient, provided we are ready to cooperate
with it. If we fail to do our share, but rather choose to rely on self-will
and self-direction, we shall not only get no help from the graces bestowed
us, we shall actually make it impossible for further graces to be given.
